<p class="megacmd-intro">Sync files between your MEGA cloud storage account and any Unraid share, powered by MEGAcmd (MEGA's official command-line client). Press the Help button (top right) at any time to see what each section below does.</p>

<p class="megacmd-warning">This plugin stores its login session and all sync/backup configuration under its appdata folder (<code>appdata/megacmd</code>). Most of that is in a hidden <code>.megaCmd</code> subfolder you won't see at a glance -- don't delete the appdata/megacmd folder to "clean up" logs or free space, or you'll be logged out and lose every sync and backup you've configured. The visible <code>server.log</code> file is the only thing safe to delete on its own; use "View recent logs" below instead if you just want to check on things.</p>

