    a download that happened as part of a sync, "UB" an upload as part of a backup, and so on.
  </blockquote>
</div>

<div class="megacmd-box">
  <h3>Current backups</h3>
  <? if (trim($backupList) !== "" && stripos($backupList, "No backup configured") === false): ?>
